The resin casing constructed to protect against vibration and impact also the watch casing has a magnetic resistant technology to protect the clock from magnetic fields. The watch face is approximately 51mm in width and is approximately 14mm in depth. This timepiece has a LED light to illuminate the watch face for optimum visibility in any lighting. Bright white clock hands against the black dial gives the watch colour, grey batons mark each of the hour markers. This GA-150-1AER has a lot of great features, the word time function displays the current time in major cities and most time zones around the globe. The stopwatch function is a great addition to this watch as it measure accurately and precise, this function allows the measuring capacity to reach to 100 hours. Speed display feature, this allows the individual to measure the average speed travelled for a single route by a simple press of a button. This Casio G-Shock also has an auto calendar which once set the calendar always shows the right time. Casio guarantee that the battery life on this particular model is to last approximately 3 years.
